{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act13d0_level_act13d0_st05","storyGroup":"act13d0","storySort":5,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"","storyName":"四月的歌","storyPic":"storyMainPic_level_act13d0_st05","storyInfo":"任务归来的四月，恰好见到了和信使交谈的安赛尔，好奇的她上前和安赛尔谈。交谈过后，她明白了一些过去不曾想到的事情。","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"activities/act13d0/level_act13d0_st05","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"USE_ITEM","costItemType":"MATERIAL","costItemId":"STORY_REVIEW_COIN","costItemCount":1,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":[],"prev":3,"next":5,"characters":["四月","罗德岛信使","安赛尔"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"中秋 四月","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_bg_bg_corridor.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/a001/m_dia_path_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"呼，今天的任务出了一身汗。","id":10,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"赶紧回宿舍洗个澡吧。","id":11,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#2","id":12},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"咦，那边的是......","id":13,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_char_365_aprl_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_002","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛信使","text":"好了，信和每一份钱都确认完毕。","id":15,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_avg_npc_002.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_212_ansel_1","name2":"avg_npc_002","focus":"1","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"那就麻烦你了。","id":17,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_212_ansel_1","name2":"avg_npc_002","focus":"2","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛信使","text":"哈哈，放心吧，你都算是老客户了。老实说，你的家人都要认识我了。","id":19,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_avg_npc_002.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛信使","text":"不过你也有一段时间没有回去了吧？不考虑回去一趟吗？伯父见到我肯定又要让我催你回一趟雷姆必拓了。","id":20,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_avg_npc_002.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛信使","text":"虽然我也是一年都在外面跑的人没有资格说什么，不过多少信可都比不上你亲自回去。","id":21,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_avg_npc_002.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_212_ansel_1","name2":"avg_npc_002","focus":"1","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"......我知道，只是这边还有病人需要我。","id":23,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"等空闲下来后，我会回去的。","id":24,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_212_ansel_1","name2":"avg_npc_002","focus":"2","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛信使","text":"好吧，我想你在这方面也是能够把握住的，就不多说什么了。","id":26,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_avg_npc_002.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛信使","text":"好，那我再去确认一下别的信件就差不多出发了。","id":27,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_avg_npc_002.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛信使","text":"特产呢，还是老样子？","id":28,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_avg_npc_002.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_212_ansel_1","name2":"avg_npc_002","focus":"1","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"嗯，帮我带一盒我家楼下小店里卖的薄荷糖吧。","id":30,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_212_ansel_1","name2":"avg_npc_002","focus":"2","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛信使","text":"好好。","id":32,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_avg_npc_002.png"},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":33},{"type":"character","id":34},{"type":"dialog","id":35},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":36},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_bg_bg_corridor.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":37},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":38},{"type":"character","name":"char_212_ansel_1","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"大伯，对不起......","id":40,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"......","id":42,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":43},{"type":"character","id":44},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":45},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_bg_bg_corridor.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":46},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":47},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"原来罗德岛上也有信使。","id":49,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"你是......","id":51,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#6","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"我是新加入的干员，代号是四月，叫我四月就好。","id":53,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/38/Avg_char_365_aprl_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#6","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"你好，四月，我是医疗部的安赛尔。","id":55,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"罗德岛上有不少信使哦，而且像刚才那位那样的信使并不是我们的干员，他们是专为罗德岛上的人服务的信使。","id":56,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#2","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"有什么区别吗？","id":58,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_char_365_aprl_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#2","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"有的，虽然选择成为我们干员的人之中也有信使存在，啊你认识安洁莉娜小姐吗？","id":60,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"认识，那个和我差不多大的信使女孩子吧？","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"嗯，首先，会加入罗德岛的信使通常是因为感染得病，选择用成为干员的方式抵消医疗费用，安洁莉娜小姐就是这样的例子。","id":64,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"啊，那我也是。","id":66,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"嗯，毕竟针对矿石病的医疗费用不管怎么说都不能算低，舰内有不少各行各业的人也都是因为类似的理由留在这里的。","id":68,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"那不就和成为这里的信使差不多了吗？","id":70,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"啊哈哈，这方面果然容易被误解，其实不是的。","id":72,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"信使这个职业，因为与人直接接触比较少，而且本身就需要到处跑，因此即使成为感染者也是可以继续的。","id":73,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"或者说，大部分人根本不知道给自己送信寄信的是不是感染者......","id":74,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"总之，他们是可以继续在自己原本的活动范围内工作的，只要定期来到罗德岛接受治疗就好了。","id":75,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#2","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"咦，但是这样不就等于在做自己的事吗？","id":77,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_char_365_aprl_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#2","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":78},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"当然，我们对这样的信使干员通常也会发出一些类似长期外勤的任务。","id":79,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"而且他们通常也会把罗德岛当成自己的一个驿站，如果自己活动的范围内有我们的干员的亲属或者朋友，那肯定是可以拜托他们寄信的。","id":80,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"但是像我这样，需要定期向家里寄信的人，就很难期待他们。","id":81,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"虽然实际上罗德岛上目前来自雷姆必拓的信使也很少就是了。","id":82,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"这样啊，不过还是感觉没什么约束力......要是在我过去呆的公司，这种事情完全是无法想象的。","id":84,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"哪种事情？","id":86,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"就是员工拥有自己的自由啊，我觉得肯定会有那种只来了一次就再也没来过的人吧？","id":88,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"你还真敏锐，这种情况确实偶尔会发生，我们当然也会追责，但不管怎么说，不能放着病人不管。","id":90,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#6","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"安赛尔医生你真是好人。","id":92,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/38/Avg_char_365_aprl_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#6","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"过奖了，我只是想着能帮一个是一个而已。","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"不过这么说的话，确实罗德岛专属的信使是有必要的。","id":96,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"我都没有想过这样的事。","id":97,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"咦，四月，你也是雷姆必拓出身吧？","id":99,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"嗯，南边的钢铁萝卜城。","id":101,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"啊，我有听说过，你们城市每年的矿石产量都名列前茅。","id":103,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#6","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"是啊，这是我们城的骄傲，虽然我没什么感觉就是了。","id":105,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/38/Avg_char_365_aprl_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#6","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"我是铁腕城出身的。你在家乡没有什么要联络的亲人吗？","id":107,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"没有哦。","id":109,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"我的父母在我小的时候就因为矿难去世了，我是被他们供职的公司抚养大的。","id":110,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"在成年后我就成为了这家公司的猎人，虽然工资也不算高，不过也还算过得去，直到我感染了矿石病......","id":112,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"......对不起。","id":114,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#6","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"没事啦。","id":116,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/38/Avg_char_365_aprl_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#6","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"不过我记得雷姆必拓的公司对感染者的待遇并不差吧？","id":118,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"因为雷姆必拓的矿业很发达，这里的人比起其他国家的人本来接触矿石病的几率就要高不少......","id":119,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"我一开始也是这么想的，但是实际体验下来我才知道我错了。","id":121,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"他们表面上说得有各种福利，但其实暗中各种克扣，而且在知道你得了矿石病后，工作机会也会越来越少。","id":122,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"像我这样一个人生活的矿石病患者，在那里是活不下去的。","id":123,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"竟然是这样......我都不知道。","id":125,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"难怪以前那些得了矿石病的工友有很多都不知道去哪里了......","id":126,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"反正，公司身份也注销了，租的房子也退了，雷姆必拓已经没有我的容身之所啦。","id":128,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#6","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"哎呀，医生你别露出这副表情，我很讨厌被人觉得可怜的。","id":130,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/38/Avg_char_365_aprl_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"而且我这不是来到罗德岛了嘛。","id":132,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"说的也是。","id":134,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"比起这个，我刚才看到你寄信时表情有点难过，是发生了什么事吗？","id":136,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#2","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":137},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"啊，要是是什么秘密就不用告诉我了，我也不会跟别人说这件事的！","id":139,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_char_365_aprl_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#2","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"......","id":141,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"四月，你吃过午饭了吗？","id":142,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"还没有，我刚任务回来，打算洗个澡再去的。","id":144,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"那我请你吃午饭吧，这个话题说起来会有些长。","id":146,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#3","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"嗯？好呀。","id":148,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_char_365_aprl_3.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":149},{"type":"character","id":150},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":151},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/98/Avg_bg_bg_canteen.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":152},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":153},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#2","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"哇，医生你吃得好健康啊。","id":155,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_char_365_aprl_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#2","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"职业习惯而已，还有叫我安赛尔就好了，我们的年龄应该没有差很多。","id":157,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#6","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"好~","id":159,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/38/Avg_char_365_aprl_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#6","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"先吃饭吧，吃完可以慢慢说。","id":161,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"嗯。","id":163,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":164},{"type":"dialog","id":165},{"type":"character","id":166},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":167},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/98/Avg_bg_bg_canteen.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":168},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":169},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":170,"musicid":1},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"......虽然我嘴上总是说着见不到家人很遗憾，其实我是有些不想回去的。","id":172,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#2","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"为什么？","id":174,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_char_365_aprl_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#2","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"回去会变得很麻烦。","id":176,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"我家有三个哥哥和一个妹妹，但我们的父母也走得很早，妈妈是肺病，爸爸是劳累过度。","id":177,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"不过和你不同的是，他们走的时候，我的三个哥哥都已经可以出去工作了。","id":178,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"只有我还是孩子，所以爸爸在去世时将我过继给了大伯，而把妹妹交给了叔叔。","id":179,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"啊，确实这样的事也不少见，我家要是有亲戚的话，应该也会是这样吧。","id":181,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"我记得我爸爸说过，我家的亲戚都去别的城市了。","id":183,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"所以你不想回去是因为大伯对你不好吗？","id":184,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"不是。伯父是一家小公司的经理，为人比较正经严肃，但是对我很好，他是真的把我当做自己的儿子看待的。","id":186,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"只是......","id":187,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"他并不希望我成为医生。","id":188,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#2","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"啊。","id":190,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_char_365_aprl_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#2","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"我从小就在大伯的公司帮忙，大伯原本是希望我以后能够接替他的位置的。","id":192,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"但我却不顾他的反对选择了成为医生，并且来到了罗德岛这么遥远的地方。","id":193,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#2","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":194},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"啊？难道安赛尔你是离家出走的？！","id":196,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_char_365_aprl_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#2","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"啊哈哈，不是不是，还没有到那个地步。","id":198,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"从我选择学医到来到罗德岛之间，还是有一段时间的。","id":199,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"在那段时间里，我和大伯聊了许多次，也争吵过。","id":200,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"大伯最后还是同意了我的选择。","id":201,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"也不是不能理解诶，毕竟在雷姆必拓当医生感觉很难生存的样子。","id":203,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"嗯，一方面是起步很难。另一方面，想要精进也很难。","id":205,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"很多矿区配备的医生往往只具有最基础的医术。","id":206,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"生活肯定是没有在大伯的公司工作稳定，而且也很难找到工作。","id":207,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"其实我也想过很多次听从大伯的安排，老实说，大伯的公司并不差。","id":208,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"而且，大伯为了我的生活付出了许多，我不应该辜负他的期待。","id":209,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"说是这么说啦，但人有想做的事很正常啊。","id":211,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"你大伯算是很好嘞，我爸爸妈妈要是还在，遇到这种事大概是不会同意的。","id":213,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"嗯，总之我最后还是坚持了自己的选择。","id":215,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"但大伯是个藏不住心事的人，他在公司待了半辈子，他始终还是希望我能够回去继承他的事业。","id":216,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"我过去两次回去的时候，总是会有些难受。","id":217,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"而且我的哥哥们其实更加反对这件事，只是我有给他们寄钱所以他们不会说些什么而已。","id":218,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"反倒是我的妹妹还算是比较支持我。","id":219,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"对我来说是比较遥远的事情诶。","id":221,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"只能说，各有各的烦恼吧。","id":223,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"我相信自己在做很好的事情，罗德岛的待遇也很好。","id":224,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"但这种事就......没有办法。","id":225,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"无论如何，我都没有办法解决大伯心中的遗憾。","id":226,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"我只能在自己的事业上更加努力，做到更好。","id":227,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"直到有一天我能够挺起胸膛说，“大伯你看，我救了很多人，我为解决矿石病做出了很多贡献。”","id":228,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"......虽然大概到那时，我也只是能够有底气面对大伯而已了吧。","id":229,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"没想到安赛尔你看起来柔柔弱弱的，其实也想了不少诶。","id":231,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"我都不知道你这么说是在夸我还是在损我了。","id":233,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#6","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"当然是夸你啦。","id":235,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/38/Avg_char_365_aprl_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#6","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"哈哈，好吧。","id":237,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"所以说，安赛尔你其实还是想回去的吧？","id":239,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"......是啊。","id":241,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"虽然跟着罗德岛去各种地方开阔视野很好，但是不管怎么说，那里始终是我的家乡。","id":242,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"我还是会怀念巨大的烟囱，嘈杂的机器运转声，矿工们的喊号子声，吵闹的街道......","id":243,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"说不定未来有一天，我也会离开罗德岛，回到我的家乡，在那里做一名医生。","id":244,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"这样啊......","id":246,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"怎么了？","id":248,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"没什么，我只是在想，虽然嘴上说着我一点也不牵挂雷姆必拓了，我会不会其实也是想回去的呢。","id":250,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"安赛尔，你知道我代号的来历吗？","id":251,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"不是月份吗？","id":253,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"是，也不是。这其实是一首歌的名字，一首有关春天的歌的名字。","id":255,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"我一直觉得我是不喜欢雷姆必拓的，你提到的这些，我都不喜欢。","id":257,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"在我的记忆里，家乡总是灰蒙蒙，黑压压的，压得我有些喘不过气来。","id":258,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"在没有感染矿石病的时候，生活也不是很轻松。","id":259,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"每天都要去公司报道，有任务就会跟着队伍一起走。","id":260,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"虽然有钱赚，但是外面的条件很差，而且经常一出去就是十几天，有时候甚至一两个月也不奇怪。","id":261,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"而没有任务时，我也没有什么特别想做的事。","id":262,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"喜欢的乐队都是其他国家的，想要的化妆品只能在杂志上看看。","id":263,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"而且工厂多导致空气不好，于是我总是要在护肤品上花更多的精力。","id":264,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"还有工厂和街上声音太大，我半夜经常会被吵醒。","id":265,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#4","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":266},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"你敢信吗，公寓的设施也比较差，有时候洗澡洗一半居然能够突然没水！","id":268,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/8d/Avg_char_365_aprl_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#4","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"呃，那确实是不太好的回忆......","id":270,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"不过，当我真的去回想的时候，也会想起一些好事。","id":272,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"公司虽然黑心，不过也照顾了我许多年，我不知道上层究竟是怎么想的，但我记得我去找公司的人问这件事时他们脸上不忍的表情。","id":273,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"邻居虽然，不过也帮过我的忙。楼上那个平时总是对别人很凶的佩罗爷爷，在知道我得了矿石病后偶尔会给我送点菜。","id":274,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"啊，不过楼下的罗罗阿婆真的很讨人厌，见到我就要冲我吐口水。","id":275,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"楼下的超市里轮替的食物也都挺好吃的，啊，这么说起来，那里的丸子我好像没在别的地方看到卖过，那个很好吃诶。","id":276,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#3","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"当然啦，小时候和爸爸妈妈一起的生活也很快乐。","id":278,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_char_365_aprl_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"我懂了，这就是所谓的回忆滤镜吧！","id":279,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_char_365_aprl_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#3","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"哈哈哈，或许吧。","id":281,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"但是无论如何，我想，我们终究都是无法抛弃自己的出身的。","id":282,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"我来到罗德岛后，了解到了这片大地的广阔，知道了还有许许多多更加精彩的生活方式。","id":283,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"我也想过尝试一下别的生活，比如成为近卫干员或者术师干员，或者去做文职工作，我都想过。","id":284,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"而且我应该是可以选择新的生活的，没有人会阻止我。","id":285,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"但最终我还是继续在做医生。","id":286,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"因为我出生在雷姆必拓，我成长在工人们之间，除非我某天忽然失忆，否则我想我是无法完全否定自己的过去的。","id":287,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"说到失忆，我好像听说博士也是失忆了？","id":289,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":290},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"啊，嗯，这并不是秘密。","id":291,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"那按照安赛尔你的说法，你觉得博士能够选择新的生活吗？","id":293,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"......我觉得很难吧。","id":295,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"我不了解博士的过去，但阿米娅和凯尔希医生都知道他，很多人都知道他。","id":296,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"我想，博士也会有许多身不由己的时候吧。","id":297,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"所以或许是这样，即使是失忆了，我们依然很难摆脱自己的过去。","id":298,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":299},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"唔，感觉话题有些变掉了 ，从家乡变成了过去。","id":300,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"不过也是，家乡本来就是一个人的过去里最重要的一部分。","id":301,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"是的，我想，重要的并不是家乡本身，而是在家乡度过的时间在我们身上留下了怎样的痕迹。","id":303,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"虽然我可以抛弃这种痕迹，但我还是选择了接纳。","id":304,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"那么，你呢？","id":305,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"我啊......","id":307,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"嗯......","id":308,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"不知道，我还没想好。","id":310,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"没关系，我们还年轻，还有很多时间去想这个问题。","id":312,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"但我想，我至少不是为了逃离那种生活才选择离开雷姆必拓的。","id":314,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"如果还能在那里生活，我应该还是会继续生活下去的，我只是不得不离开。","id":315,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"成为感染者这件事确实让我吃了许多苦头，但我没有办法就这么去讨厌别人，去说我憎恨雷姆必拓。","id":316,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"很正常的，一个人就算变成了感染者，他的想法也不是立刻就会变化的。","id":318,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"有关这一点，你在罗德岛生活更长一段时间后应该能有更深的体会，至少现在，我们只需要聊有关家乡和过去的话题就好。","id":319,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"嗯，总之，我想，我应该其实也是属于接纳的类型吧。","id":321,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"我还是不会说我喜欢雷姆必拓，说我喜欢钢铁萝卜城。","id":322,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#5","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"但我想永远不会忘记，每当我烦恼的时候，我就会去公寓的天台。","id":324,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"我住的公寓不算高，周围有更多其他高楼。","id":325,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"我有时候会觉得周围的高楼就像栅栏，它们困住了我，而我头顶的那一块天空，就是我唯一能看到的风景。","id":326,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_365_aprl_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"但这反而会给我一种安心感，因为我不需要很大的空间，我也不想要很多的选择，这种狭小的感觉对我来说反而正好。","id":328,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"我会在那里转一圈，看一看住在周围的人们都在干什么，有时候会看到很有趣的事，有时候没有，都没关系。","id":329,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"然后，我会躺在天台的正中央，戴上耳机，播放我最喜欢的《四月》，想着那些有的没的的事，美美地睡一会儿。","id":330,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#6","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":331},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"等我睡醒的时候，大部分的烦恼也就烟消云散啦。","id":332,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/38/Avg_char_365_aprl_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#6","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":333},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"听起来很舒服啊。","id":334,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"是啊，我现在有时也会想找一个这样的地方睡一会儿，不过罗德岛的甲板太空旷了，找不到我想要的感觉。","id":336,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"或许你可以去找一个叫克洛丝的干员，她对于寻找偷懒的地方很有经验。","id":338,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#3","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"真的吗？那太好了，我之后去问问她！","id":340,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_char_365_aprl_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":341},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"不过这么一说，确实变得有些想要回去了诶。","id":342,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#6","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":343},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"都怪你。","id":344,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/38/Avg_char_365_aprl_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#6","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":345},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"哈哈，那可真是抱歉了。","id":346,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":347},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"不过暂时还是算了。我还是新人，刚加入就请假可不好。","id":348,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#2","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"啊，我想到了！","id":350,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_char_365_aprl_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"安赛尔，你拜托寄信的那个信使走了吗？","id":351,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_char_365_aprl_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#2","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"2","id":352},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安赛尔","text":"应该还没有，他会待到明天。","id":353,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_char_212_ansel_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"char_212_ansel_1","focus":"1","id":354},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"好，那我去找他！","id":355,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":356},{"type":"character","id":357},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":358},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_bg_bg_corridor.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":359},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":360},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.6","id":361},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":362},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":363},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":364},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"信使先生！你是要去雷姆必拓的对吧？","id":365,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"avg_npc_002","focus":"2","id":366},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛信使","text":"对，卡特斯的小姐，你要寄信吗？","id":367,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_avg_npc_002.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"avg_npc_002","focus":"1","id":368},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"叫我四月就好。我不是来寄信的，不过我可以拜托你一件事吗？","id":369,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"avg_npc_002","focus":"2","id":370},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛信使","text":"什么？","id":371,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_avg_npc_002.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"avg_npc_002","focus":"1","id":372},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"你去雷姆必拓的时候，能不能劳烦你去一座高楼的楼顶，帮我拍一下那里看到的风景？","id":373,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","name2":"avg_npc_002","focus":"2","id":374},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛信使","text":"嗯？这个请求还真是奇怪。","id":375,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_avg_npc_002.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛信使","text":"......不过听起来不是很麻烦，应该可以。","id":376,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_avg_npc_002.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl#3","name2":"avg_npc_002","focus":"1","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"好，那就麻烦你了！","id":378,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_char_365_aprl_3.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":379},{"type":"character","id":380},{"type":"character","name":"char_365_aprl","id":381},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"家乡，过去......原来我也没有自己想的那么不在乎。","id":383,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"四月","text":"唔，不过，比起这个，我还是先去找那个叫克洛丝的人好了，比起回不回去，还是能不能找到放松的好地方比较现实！","id":384,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_char_365_aprl.png"},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":385},{"type":"dialog","id":386},{"type":"character","id":387},{"type":"image","id":388}],"characters":["四月","罗德岛信使","安赛尔"]}